<%- include('partials/header') %>

<main class="about-page">

    <section class="about-hero">

        <h1><%= title %></h1>

        <p class="about-intro">
            Welcome to our Used Car Dealership, your trusted destination
            for quality pre-owned vehicles. We are dedicated to helping
            customers find reliable cars, trucks, vans, and SUVs at
            competitive prices.
        </p>

    </section>

    <section class="about-section">

        <h2>🚗 Our Mission</h2>

        <p>
            Our mission is to provide dependable vehicles and exceptional
            customer service while making the car-buying experience simple,
            transparent, and stress-free. We believe every customer deserves
            a vehicle they can trust and a dealership they can rely on.
        </p>

    </section>

    <section class="about-section">

        <h2>📖 Our Story</h2>

        <p>
            Since opening our doors in 2010, we have built a reputation for
            honesty, reliability, and customer satisfaction. What started as
            a small dealership has grown into a trusted automotive resource
            serving drivers throughout the community.
        </p>

    </section>

    <section class="about-section">

        <h2>⭐ Why Customers Choose Us</h2>

        <div class="about-features">

            <div class="feature-card">
                <h3>✅ Quality Inventory</h3>
                <p>
                    Carefully selected vehicles inspected for quality and reliability.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-card">
                <h3>💰 Fair Pricing</h3>
                <p>
                    Competitive prices that provide excellent value for every budget.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-card">
                <h3>📋 Vehicle History</h3>
                <p>
                    Access to vehicle information and transparent records.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-card">
                <h3>🤝 Customer Service</h3>
                <p>
                    Friendly staff committed to helping you find the right vehicle.
                </p>
            </div>

        </div>

    </section>

    <section class="about-section">

        <h2>🛠️ Additional Services</h2>

        <p>
            Beyond vehicle sales, we help customers manage service requests,
            browse dealership locations, submit reviews, and stay connected
            through our customer support system.
        </p>

    </section>

    <section class="about-cta">

        <h2>Find Your Next Vehicle Today</h2>

        <p>
            Explore our inventory and discover why drivers continue to trust
            our dealership for their automotive needs.
        </p>

        <div class="cta-buttons">
            <a href="/vehicles" class="btn-primary">Browse Vehicles</a>
            <a href="/contact" class="btn-secondary">Contact Us</a>
        </div>

    </section>

</main>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>